PinkSwap is a DEFI application built on the EOS chain by PINK Community (Pink Dream Manor). PINKPINK has a total amount of 1 billion and will never be issued again. It is the PinkSwap token under Pink Dream Manor, the governance token of Pink Dream Manor, and the proof of the rights and interests of Pink Dream Manor.

Pink Dream Manor is a seascape manor set up in Hainan Island, China in the future. PINK advocates sound financial management and uses the token distribution model of financial management that is mining to ensure that all tokens are distributed fairly and fairly to financial customers and community contributors! We are positioned as the fund manager of digital assets in the blockchain world, the dream practitioner of Binhai theme manor hotel, elderly care, green ecological farm, and love for students!
